<center>and any true magician would find magic easy.

<voice_0x0100124B><se_high><center>You may think that neither you nor I know.

<center>But if you ask me...

<voice_0x0100124D><se_def><center>I am not an ancestor who has inherited magic.

<center>but they will one day
